  "title": "Product Manager (IT Sales)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Own product portfolio revenue, targets and forecast</p></li><li><p>Drive sales through close engagement with sales teams and channel partners</p></li><li><p>Act as product and commercial SME to support deals, pricing and BOM</p></li><li><p>Enable channel partners through product training and positioning</p></li><li><p>Manage vendor relationships, joint business planning and promotions</p></li><li><p>Work with Marketing on go-to-market activities</p></li><li><p>Monitor pricing, margins, and inventory performance<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>1–5 years in Cybersecurity / IT / Technology Distribution</p></li><li><p>Strong sales orientation and comfortable with targets and revenue ownership</p></li><li><p>Background in Sales Engineering, Channel Management or Product roles preferred</p></li><li><p>Good commercial judgement with the ability to translate technical value into business outcomes</p></li><li><p>Strong communication, presentation, and stakeholder management skills<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>To Apply, please kindly email your updated resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:weizhe.teoh@tg-hr.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>weizhe.teoh@tg-hr.com</strong></a></p><p><strong>Regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>CEI: R25127749</strong></p><p><strong>EA License: 14C7275</strong>\n</p>",
